  <summary date="2023-03-28T12:29:01Z" status="Introduced in House">Financing Lead Out of Water Act of 2023

This bill allows the issuance of tax-exempt private activity bonds to finance the replacement of any privately-owned portion of a lead service line in a public water system. Specifically, the bill provides that the use of proceeds from such bonds for replacement of a lead service line does not constitute private business use.</summary>
